<h2 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h2><h3 id="补充样式"><a href="#补充样式" class="headerlink" title="补充样式"></a>补充样式</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font size=<span class="number">5</span>&gt;&lt;/font&gt; 字体大小</span><br><span class="line">&lt;a style=<span class="string">&quot;color:black&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 字体颜色</span><br><span class="line">&lt;a style=<span class="string">&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 取消链接下划线</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="页内跳转"><a href="#页内跳转" class="headerlink" title="页内跳转"></a>页内跳转</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;a href=<span class="string">&quot;#Name&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 跳转的起点</span><br><span class="line">&lt;a name=<span class="string">&quot;Name&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 跳转的终点</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

